    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_enbook-zlib-o.O-21353024.pdf_39_24",
    "text": "> Andonstar AD407 HDMI Digital Microscope (SKU 19079) www.elektor.com/19079",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5277207326438108,
      0.6787790698818988,
      0.9301847980885646,
      0.7005813952636608
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_enbook-zlib-o.O-21353024.pdf_39",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_enbook-zlib-o.O-21353024.pdf_39_7",
    "text": "Don't Expect to Identify Everything!",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.07186859086593149,
      0.6874999997733083,
      0.3798767928609679,
      0.702132936281245
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_enbook-zlib-o.O-21353024.pdf_39",
    "order": 21
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_enbook-zlib-o.O-21353024.pdf_39_8",
    "text": "I have a bag of transistors labelled 0V8F which have stubbornly refused to be identified. SMD components can be difficult or impossible to identify, as they often have shortened part numbers on them. Even with the considerable resources on the internet, they are not easy.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0698151920189558,
      0.7048611110958863,
      0.5010266966874097,
      0.7587209303603493
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_enbook-zlib-o.O-21353024.pdf_39",
    "order": 22
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_enbook-zlib-o.O-21353024.pdf_39_25",
    "text": "> Miniware DT71 Mini Digital Tweezers (SKU 19422) www.elektor.com/19422",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5338809149573921,
      0.7135416664694451,
      0.8829568743649898,
      0.735465116089937
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_enbook-zlib-o.O-21353024.pdf_39",
    "order": 23
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_enbook-zlib-o.O-21353024.pdf_39_26",
